{"tid":2008104,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我就黎比啲傻系蚊搞到我神經失常","createTime":"2020-05-08T19:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T22:26:23.000Z","uid":332913,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"239539502ed3669c073d9aef0617a605bc32e1f3","tid":2008104,"uid":332913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"由上年開始成日失眠，有時連食褪黑色素都搞唔掂，前排開始想決心較返好個生理時鐘。<br />\n點知啲傻系蚊就喺依段時間出現左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔訓，佢地匿埋唔比我見到；我熄晒燈準備訓，佢地居然咬我；我唔理佢地打算照訓，佢地就言語恐嚇我 : 嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯；我開返燈，thanks 又匿埋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失眠+睡眠質素差+晚晚比啲傻系黎騷擾<br />\n我諗我就快癲，我真係好想殺晒佢地<br />\n利申: 唔敢打死佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa1e0c1f9a81887a897b3252dd5cdbdbd65b26f","tid":2008104,"uid":311368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"幻覺嚟嘅啫 嚇我唔到嘅"},{"pid":"21d61f27baeaed2f484a05a4656475c432760b7c","tid":2008104,"uid":332913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aa1e0c1f9a81887a897b3252dd5cdbdbd65b26f","tid":2008104,"uid":311368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"幻覺嚟嘅啫 嚇我唔到嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:23:59.000Z","msg":"嚇到我就黎喊 再係咁落去 我會痴線"},{"pid":"cbbe3b638e565034924d784e2e6c863712ef9323","tid":2008104,"uid":311368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21d61f27baeaed2f484a05a4656475c432760b7c","tid":2008104,"uid":332913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aa1e0c1f9a81887a897b3252dd5cdbdbd65b26f","tid":2008104,"uid":311368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"幻覺嚟嘅啫 嚇我唔到嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:23:59.000Z","msg":"嚇到我就黎喊 再係咁落去 我會痴線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:25:08.000Z","msg":"叫你老母岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5133ae86aa3945b604733a2d66232a3b0a69c